      "description": "This vehicle strikes a fine balance between aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, showing only minor, expected road wear upon close inspection, while the wheels remain free of major curbing. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats are supportive and free of significant wear, and all electronic systems\u2014including the infotainment and driver-assist features\u2014function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, supported by a documented history of regular oil changes and a recent brake service. It offers a tight, responsive driving experience that feels much younger than its mileage suggests. This is a dependable, well-cared-for example that is ready for immediate daily use.",
