    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and ready for its next adventure! It shows a little bit of character from its time on the road, but it drives beautifully and has been super well-loved. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, quick sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to be a total bargain for someone looking for a dependable ride. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it\u2014I'd love to find it a great new home!",
