      "description": "Up for sale is a 2017 Ford Mustang Shelby GT350, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the 5.2L Voodoo V8 featuring a flat-plane crankshaft that enables a stratospheric 8,250 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a Tremec TR-3160 6-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential with a 3.73 final drive ratio. The chassis is equipped with the MagneRide Damping System for superior lateral grip, complemented by a high-performance Brembo braking suite with 15.5-inch front rotors. This vehicle has been maintained with technical rigor, ensuring the powertrain and cooling systems remain in peak operating condition for the next owner.",
